Armored Aircraft Carriers are aircraft carriers that adopted the armored flight decks and armor belt. There are only four carriers in this class: [[Taihou]], [[Shoukaku|Shoukaku Kai Ni A]], [[Zuikaku|Zuikaku Kai Ni A]] and [[Saratoga|Saratoga Mk.II Mod.2]].


*Unlike Standard Aircraft Carriers, the Armored Aircraft Carriers '''can still launch their aircrafts when having sustained {{color|orange|moderate damage (中破)}}.'''
*{{color|lime|Green}}: Outstanding
*{{color|gold|Yellow}}: Great
* All Armored Aircraft Carriers have 4 slots.
* Since the Luck Stat is difficult to modernize, it is listed as Base(Max).

