* [[Taihou]] is the only Aircraft Carrier that starts out as an Armored Aircraft Carrier by default, and thus can launch planes at {{color|orange|中破 (moderate damage)}}, though her repair costs are higher. She also has high armor and plane count.
* [[Shoukaku#Third_Upgrade_.28Reversible.29|Shoukaku Kai Ni A]] is the second Armored Aircraft Carrier implemented in game, and is an optional upgrade from [[Shoukaku#Second_Upgrade|Shoukaku Kai Ni]]. She has the highest Firepower, and the second highest Anti-Air, Armor, Health and Evasion of the non-LSC or Event only obtainable CVBs. However she loses her evenly spread plane count after the remodel.
*[[Zuikaku#Third_Upgrade_.28Reversible.29|Zuikaku Kai Ni A]] is the third Armored Aircraft Carrier implemented in game, and is an optional upgrade from [[Zuikaku#Second_Upgrade|Zuikaku Kai Ni]]. She has the highest stats out of the non-LSC or Event only obtainable Armored Aircraft Carriers (aside from Firepower) but her remodel level is the highest as well. Her plane count is also spread less evenly.
** Both [[Shoukaku Kai Ni A]] and [[Zuikaku Kai Ni A]] can be remodeled again to return their to the [[Shoukaku#Second Upgrade|Shoukaku Kai Ni]] / [[Zuikaku#Second Upgrade|Zuikaku Kai Ni]] version, though this costs resources and reduces modernization like any other remodel.
* [[Saratoga_Mk.II_Mod.2#Third_Upgrade_.28Reversible.29|Saratoga/Mk.II Mod.2]] is the only foreign Armored Aircraft Carrier in the game. She can boast that both her Anti-Air, Health, Armor and plane count are the best of the ship type. However, she is also the only one that can only be obtained through LSC or event drop.
